/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>美泉宫</a></span></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1838203713\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">大量图片在正文哦！</p><div data-seq=\"1693903521\" data-index=\"2\" class=\"article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\"><h2 class=\"t9\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;\"><span class=\"_j_anchor\" style=\"line-height: 50px; display: block;\">写在开头</span></h2></div><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"1693903522\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10174.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"捷克\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">捷克</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10175.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_mdd\" data-kw=\"奥地利\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">奥地利</a>&nbsp;这次行程是疫情前最后一次出境旅行，当时的我们只是把它当作每年一次的长途出境旅行并不知道之后这几年不要说是出境了，连出市都会成为一个难题（此处只有一声长叹）。<br/><br/>当时出境时只是每天简单的记录一下见闻和趣事，回国后也没有写游记（主要还是因为拖延症谁知道这一拖就是四年）。最近得到疫情准备开放的消息，估计恢复成昨日的样貌指日可待，一直想把这篇境外游记整理成篇也算是填补了一个大坑。</p><p><br/></p>', '2022-12-30 16:44:29', '2', '002');

